rComments: I had the chance to take Dr. Pinks POL340 - International Law class over the summer. He is an amazing professor who cares for his students and their future. He gives very clear and informative lectures. He is very well versed in Political Science, particularly Human Rights and Water Rights. Hes willing to sit down and talk to you as long as need

Professor Ross Pink's lectures are engaging and interesting. His class includes groupwork and the chance to present on topics related to the course, Very helpful professor as well. He is open minded always ready to give his time during his office hours to explain important concepts or give career advice. Would definitely recommend his courses!
